  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00356', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-110-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果電動機車大幅降價，則下列敘述何者正確？', '["汽油機車的需求上升", "汽油機車的供給減少", "腳踏車的需求上升", "汽油機車市場的生產者剩餘上升"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bec6315ccf2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c6a2f8035359", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "141", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00357', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-110-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '若一追求效用極大化的消費者擁有固定預算，用於消費兩種財貨x與y，邊際效用分別表示為MUx 與MUy，兩財貨的價格分別為Px與Py，則下列敘述何者正確？', '["消費者總效用最大的必要條件為MUx=MUy", "當(MUx/Px)>(MUy/Py)時，消費者應增加y的消費", "若Px=Py，則兩種財貨消費數量應相等", "若MUx與MUy均為固定常數，則總效用極大時，消費者可能只消費其中一種財貨"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bec6315ccf2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c6a2f8035359", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "141", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00358', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-110-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設一消費者僅消費X與Y兩種財貨，效用函數為U(X,Y)=X0.2Y0.3，若此消費者所得為100，則其 在效用極大化時，會花多少錢購買財貨X？', '["20", "30", "40", "60"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bec6315ccf2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c6a2f8035359", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "141", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00359', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-110-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '若廠商生產產品的兩要素可以完全替代，而X要素的價格高於Y要素，若X要素使用量為X軸，Y 要素使用量為Y軸，則其擴張線應該為：', '["通過原點的垂直線", "通過原點的水平線", "通過原點的45度線", "斜率為負一的直線"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bec6315ccf2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c6a2f8035359", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "141", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
